### List stock transfers
GET http://localhost:3100/api/stock-transfers
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager

### Create stock transfer draft
POST http://localhost:3100/api/stock-transfers
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager

{
  "fromLocationId": "{{fromLocationId}}",
  "toLocationId": "{{toLocationId}}",
  "notes": "Move helmets into workshop",
  "lines": [
    {
      "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Send stock transfer
POST http://localhost:3100/api/stock-transfers/{{stockTransferId}}/send
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager

### Receive stock transfer
POST http://localhost:3100/api/stock-transfers/{{stockTransferId}}/receive
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager

### Cancel stock transfer
POST http://localhost:3100/api/stock-transfers/{{stockTransferId}}/cancel
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager
